text: Jyrki Tapani Katainen (born 14 October 1971) is a Finnish politician. He was the Prime Minister of Finland from June 2011 to June 2014. He is also the chairman of the National Coalition Party. ==References== ==Other websites== * Jyrki Katainen's home page * National Coalition Party of Finland Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Finland Category:Deputy Prime Ministers of Finland
